android.provider
接口 OpenableColumns

public interface OpenableColumns

These are standard columns for openable URIs. (See Intent.CATEGORY_OPENABLE.) If possible providers that have openable URIs should support these columns. To find the content type of a URI use ContentResolver.getType(android.net.Uri) as normal.

字段摘要
static String DISPLAY_NAME
          The human-friendly name of file.
static String SIZE
          The number of bytes in the file identified by the openable URI.
 

字段详细信息

DISPLAY_NAME

static final String DISPLAY_NAME
The human-friendly name of file. If this is not provided then the name should default to the the last segment of the file's URI.

另请参见：
常量字段值

SIZE

static final String SIZE
The number of bytes in the file identified by the openable URI. Null if unknown.
